{"tid":35788,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與13歲女非法性交　17歲男生再襲事主喊分手","createTime":"2016-12-12T10:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T04:11:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"998b408b4ab0a99a7a87bea8e19c5b1062abd482","tid":35788,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:16:07.000Z","msg":"17歲中六男生涉嫌今年6月至9月間，4度與同校的13歲女友非法性交，至今年10月男生提出分手，但他疑不滿女方繼續纏身，又涉向女方掌摑及掐頸。涉案男生今在觀塘法院承認4項與16歲以下女童非法性交罪及1項普通襲擊罪，裁判官先索取心理專家報告等多份報告，男生還押至12月13日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指，被告<span style=\"color: red;\">自幼上教會團契</span>，本身有發展遲緩症狀，不知事件可以嚴重至此，他被捕後情緒低落，想過輕生。被告父母早知被告拍拖，但自責未有警告他不得與年幼事主發生親密關係。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又解釋指，<span style=\"color: red;\">被告在襲擊女事主之前，早已決定跟她分手，但她仍繼續糾纏，被告遂在衝動下襲擊女方。裁判官聞言怒斥，「你諗住打走佢呀？」又批評：「你當對方係咩人？你自己嘅物品？財產？</span>」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161130/bkn-20161130130248640-1130_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161130%2Fbkn-20161130130248640-1130_00822_001.html&d=MR2cyq34YS3YJ7OZFMm7IxpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=c58b4cb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161130/bkn-20161130130248640-1130_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"863d24eb5e8c034883c1ae4f677e1698a67280b0","tid":35788,"uid":16842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街黎"},{"pid":"9d4b283f3a10cae0d9ea9600105b939a028d0ec8","tid":35788,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ka-sir.xyz/p/HKG_icon/Chicken/1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fka-sir.xyz%2Fp%2FHKG_icon%2FChicken%2F1.gif&h=2c47a375&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ka-sir.xyz/p/HKG_icon/Chicken/5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fka-sir.xyz%2Fp%2FHKG_icon%2FChicke